    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been climate-control garaged since day one and meticulously maintained with a 'no-expense-spared' philosophy. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring a deep, glass-like luster protected by a professional ceramic coating; you will find zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather upholstery retains its original matte finish and factory-fresh scent, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic component, button, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all work performed by certified specialists using only OEM parts. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a folder of every service receipt.",
